        <IsA>library</IsA>
        <Summary>A Python module for watching filesystems changes</Summary>
        <Description>python-inotify is a Python module for watching filesystems changes. It can be used for various kind of fs monitoring. It relies on a Linux Kernel feature (merged in kernel 2.6.13) called inotify. inotify is an event-driven notifier, its notifications are exported from kernel space to user space.</Description>
        <Archive sha1sum="9bd7fe54aecf05d85fd1b8b0c0b7293edb7777cd" type="targz">http://seb.dbzteam.org/pub/pyinotify/releases/pyinotify-0.9.4.tar.gz</Archive>
    </Source>

